  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA85">
<l>amuteṉṟun tēṉeṉṟu māḻiyā ṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>mamutaṉṟu koṇṭukantā ṉeṉṟu – mamutaṉṉa</l>
<l>coṉmālai yēttit toḻutēṉ colappaṭṭa</l>
<l>naṉmālai yētti naviṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying ‘ambrosia’, ‘honey’ and ‘the one with the discus’,</l>
<l>saying ‘the one who delighted taking the ambrosia that day’, praising</l> 
<l>with a garland of words like ambrosia I worshipped, uttering [it]</l>
<l>in praise of good Māl who is [thus] spoken of.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
